    "created_at": "2013-08-08T00:39:42Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-08-08T00:39:42Z",
    "body": "I actually agree with bblum here. There's no reason to make atomic ops unsafe if you already need unsafe code to do unsafe things with them. They're perfectly safe and well-defined.\n",
